Package arrayGenerator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayGeneratorTest<T>
    Provides some basic tests for array generators: Do the generators generate arrays of the correct size? Do the generators throw the expected negative array size exception if asked to generate an array of negative size?
    CharacterArrayGeneratorTest  
    IntegerArrayGeneratorTest  
    ScopedArrayGeneratorTest<T>
    Implements additional tests, above those defined in ArrayGeneratorTest, to check that: Values in generated arrays are within the specified arrayGenerator.scope All values in the arrayGenerator.scope are generated.
    StringArrayGeneratorTest
